<section>
  <h2 id="concerned-about-not-knowing-htmlcss">Concerned About Not Knowing HTML/CSS?</h2>

  <p>Here are some resources.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="http://learn.shayhowe.com/html-css/">Learn to Code HTML &amp; CSS by Shay Howe</a> by Shay Howe</li>
    <li><a href="http://www.htmldog.com/guides/">HTML Dog</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.codecademy.com/skills/make-a-website">Codecademy: Make a Website</a> by Codecademy</li>
  </ul>

  <p><br />
All are <strong>free</strong> and <strong>online</strong> &#8230; and relatively compact!</p>

  <p>You&#39;ll have some time to learn this, as we won&#39;t need any front-end development <em>at all</em> for about a month.</p>

</section>

